    "(2) What are students' perceptions of the advantages of AI-assisted academic writing?",
    "(3) What are students' perceptions of the challenges of AI-assisted academic writing?",
    "The findings of this study can develop a holistic understanding of GenAI's impact on academic writing and offer implications for educational AI design and instructional design by reflecting on the diverse roles expected of GenAI in academic writing and the benefits and barriers to GenAI-assisted writing perceived by students.",
    "Written communication can vary wildly across writers and genres, depending on stylistic preferences, goals, contexts, and the intended audience.",
    "In higher education settings, students are expected to learn academic writing, which includes specific writing processes, structures, and characteristics that will support their academic success."
